OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1779984666
OL,3,CFamily of innocent mother shot dead
OL,4,Coutside bar in Sheffield pay tribute
OL,5,Cto her
OL,7,FThe family of the Shanice Brookes, who
OL,8,Fwas fatally shot outside a bar in
OL,9,FSheffield city centre, have paid
OL,10,Ftribute to the much-loved mum-of-one.
OL,12,FShortly before 2.45am on Monday, 25
OL,13,FMay, Shanice was outside of One Four
OL,14,FOne bar on West Street when she was
OL,15,Fshot during an incident to which she
OL,16,Fwas an innocent bystander.
OL,18,FShanice was treated by officers and
OL,19,Fparamedics before being taken to
OL,20,Fhospital, where she died.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/9
