OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1779984666
OL,3,CFamily of innocent mother shot dead
OL,4,Coutside bar in Sheffield pay tribute
OL,5,Cto her
OL,7,FFollowing formal identification,
OL,8,FShanice's family have today paid
OL,9,Ftribute to her.
OL,11,FShanice lived in Sheffield where she
OL,12,Fworked for a local charity and was in
OL,13,Fthe process of completing a university
OL,14,Fdegree.
OL,16,FHer family said: "Shanice had the
OL,17,Fbiggest heart and the kind of energy
OL,18,Fyou could never forget.
OL,26,@xD@ROU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
