FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1779984666
OL,3,CFamily of innocent mother shot dead
OL,4,Coutside bar in Sheffield pay tribute
OL,5,Cto her
OL,7,F"She was a deeply loved daughter,
OL,8,Fgranddaughter, niece, cousin, friend
OL,9,Fand godmother, as well as being an
OL,10,Famazing mum to her son, who meant the
OL,11,Fworld to her. To her cousins, she was
OL,12,Fmore like a sister ` someone they
OL,13,Fcould always turn to for love,
OL,14,Flaughter and support.
OL,16,F"Shanice was also due to graduate from
OL,17,Funiversity, a reflection of her
OL,18,Fdetermination, ambition and the bright
OL,19,Ffuture ahead of her.
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1779984666
OL,3,CFamily of innocent mother shot dead
OL,4,Coutside bar in Sheffield pay tribute
OL,5,Cto her
OL,7,F"She could light up every room she
OL,8,Fwalked in to with her infectious
OL,9,Flaugh, beautiful soul and magical
OL,10,Faura. Shanice made people feel loved,
OL,11,Fsafe and valued simply by being
OL,12,Fherself.
OL,14,F"She was truly one of a kind and she
OL,15,Fwill be missed by all who were lucky
OL,16,Fenough to know and love her."
OL,18,FOn Tuesday, 26 May, South Yorkshire
OL,19,FPolice shared an image showing the
OL,20,Flocation of the incident and a vehicle
OL,21,Fthey believe to be involved.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUxD@]O]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/9
