OL,3,CFamily of innocent mother shot dead
OL,4,Coutside bar in Sheffield pay tribute
OL,5,Cto her
OL,7,FThey are continuing to ask those who
OL,8,Fsaw what happened in the early hours
OL,9,Fof Monday morning to come forward.
OL,11,FDetective Chief Inspector Andy Knowles
OL,12,Fsaid: "Today, we have formally
OL,13,Fidentified Shanice as the victim
OL,14,Ffatally injured in this incident, and
OL,15,Four thoughts are with her family and
OL,16,Fthe many people who knew and loved her.
OL,18,F"Shanice was a young woman who was in
OL,19,Fthe prime of her life and was simply
OL,20,Fenjoying a night out in the city
OL,21,Fcentre over the bank holiday weekend.
OL,26,@tD@GOUzD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
