OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1779984666
OL,3,CFamily of innocent mother shot dead
OL,4,Coutside bar in Sheffield pay tribute
OL,5,Cto her
OL,7,F"People often say innocent victims
OL,8,Fwere in the wrong place at the wrong
OL,9,Ftime, but Shanice was not in the wrong
OL,10,Fplace at the wrong time ` we should
OL,11,Fall be able to go on nights out and
OL,12,Fknow that we will come home safely.
OL,14,F"This incident lays bare the
OL,15,Fdevastation gun crimes causes within
OL,16,Ffamilies and communities and I want to
OL,17,Fsend a clear message to those who
OL,18,Fwitnessed the incident or have
OL,19,Finformation on those involved.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1779984666
OL,3,CFamily of innocent mother shot dead
OL,4,Coutside bar in Sheffield pay tribute
OL,5,Cto her
OL,7,F"If you saw what happened on Monday
OL,8,Fmorning, or have information about who
OL,9,Fwas involved, please do not stay
OL,10,Fsilent.
OL,12,F"Shanice's family, including her young
OL,13,Fson, are now facing the heartbreaking
OL,14,Freality that they will never see her
OL,15,Fagain. The reckless actions of others
OL,16,Fhave taken her life away from her and
OL,17,Fthe sad reality is that any of us, or
OL,18,Four loved ones, could have been the
OL,19,Fvictim of this senseless incident."
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/9
