OL,7,FPolice say a 30-year-old man and 32-
OL,8,Fyear-old woman who were arrested on
OL,9,Fsuspicion of murder near Stockport
OL,10,Fremain in custody and detectives have
OL,11,Fbeen given further time to question
OL,12,Fthem.
OL,14,FA 30-year-old man arrested on
OL,15,Fsuspicion of murder in Sheffield has
OL,16,Fnow been released and is no longer
OL,17,Fbeing treated as a suspect.
